casebody.data:
Steven SMITH
v.
WORKERS' COMPENSATION APPEAL BOARD (CONSOLIDATED FREIGHTWAYS CORPORATION OF DELAWARE) Petition of: Mary Ellen Chajkowski No. 351 WAL 2017 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. January 17, 2018

ORDER

PER CURIAM .

AND NOW, this 17th day of January, 2018, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal and the Application for Permission to File a Reply be DENIED and that Petitioner be REFERRED to the Office of Disciplinary Counsel.
